        "rich_text_kdLUhA": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>In India, wearing nose jewelry has been part of tradition. From brides walking down the aisle with a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/nose-pins\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nose Pins\">nose pin</a> that defines femininity to women wearing it every day as part of their routine, diamond nose rings are timeless. Nose adornments are believed to signify beauty. In Ayurveda, they are believed to ease menstrual pain, promote reproductive health, and ease childbirth. </p><p>Today, the style has transcended borders. From minimalist diamond nose studs gracing hollywood red carpets to bold hoops in global fashion weeks, diamond nose pin have achieved a universal appeal.</p><p>We understand that piercing the nose can be intimidating, and to alleviate your skepticism, we have created this guide to help you achieve the perfect nose piercing to radiate the beauty you are looking for.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_RmbKbx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Choose the Right Nose Pin",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Choose the Right Nose Pin</h2>",
            "custom_id": "choose",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_JLA9nG": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1.1_Nosepin.jpg",
            "text": "<p>While there are no hard and fast rules, it’s important to see how you can use your face shape to decide the best nose pin for you. If you have a round face, opt for angular or vertical designs such as nose studs for women. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "cherish-heart-diamond-nosepin",
              "classic-round-diamond-nosepin"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_M7BnLF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>They look sleek and balance the features. If you’ve a square face, you’ll love designs with curved or rounded sides. They will soften your defined angles and enhance your feminine look. If you’re blessed with an oval shape, you can choose almost any shape - circular hoops or tiny floral motifs. Nose rings are versatile and suit everyone, but you can select nose rings for nose types to accentuate your features. Choose nose studs that are tiny if you have a petite nose to balance the features. Nose pins for small nose can also be tiny floral motifs that do not overpower the look. For a broader nose, choose a clustered or geometric design that draws the attention to craftsmanship rather than to the width of the nose. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_737a7Y": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Which Metal To Choose?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Which Metal To Choose?</h2>",
            "custom_id": "metal",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_zNhcaj": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3_f3386763-7c8d-4553-8449-e239996b4b86.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_GBUNVz": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Your choice of metal defines the mood. For not triggering any allergies or skin rashes, opt for precious metals such as gold and platinum, which are not only durable, but safe for your skin. Yellow gold is the most preferred choice as it is the symbol of tradition and is versatile when it comes to nose pins. On the other hand, choose white gold or platinum for reflecting more understated luxury, effortless elegance, and minimalism. This is an ideal choice for everyday workwear. If you’re looking for a choice that effortlessly suits both western and ethnic wear, choose rose gold. With a romantic touch, rose gold looks subtle and soft.</p><p>A single diamond nose pins never fails. It is refined and timeless. Add a pop of personality and color with colored lab grown diamonds to make a subtle and unique statement. With these nuances in mind, you can choose a nose pin design with a focus on craftsmanship and elegance.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JjfRmt": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How To Wear A Nose Pin ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How To Wear A Nose Pin </h2>",
            "custom_id": "wear",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_PQf3RL": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_5b55f508-9c91-44e5-84d2-2bb0611ed2e4.jpg",
            "text": "<p>In India, many people wear a nose pin on the left. In North India, some even wear it on the right. However, there are no rules for the same. Women usually have a preference or a 'better side' in selfies, you can choose which side you like better.</p><p></p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "cluster-round-diamond-nosepin",
              "elegant-round-diamond-nosepin"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_B3WQTw": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When getting your piercing, ensure it’s done professionally with sterilized tools and high-quality nose piercing jewelry. If you’re new to it, start with a small diamond nose rings in gold or white gold to allow the piercing to heal comfortably. Once worn, the nose pin shouldn’t feel heavy or obstructive. Having a diamond nose piercing can highlight your features without overpowering them.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_HqBYGB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How To Style Your Nose Pin",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How To Style Your Nose Pin </h2><p>From minimal designs for everyday wear to festive opulence, you have to choose your pick based on the occasion. For everyday wear, choose a minimal diamond stud or a plain metal motif that sits daintily without drawing too much attention. </p><p>For festive occasions, go intricate. Think polki or small hoops (naths) inspired by culture and craftsmanship. The best diamond nose pin for grand occasions such as weddings are dangling naths with diamond detailing. For vacations and party wear, be the whimsical and quirky you. Maybe go for a butterfly nose pin for ladies or a celestial star nose pin to show your playful side, while being comfortable in these lightweight nose pins and rings. </p>",
            "custom_id": "style",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BxEngQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Care And Maintenance",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Care And Maintenance</h2>",
            "custom_id": "care",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_JkqtLw": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4_9f05fbdd-a42d-45bf-8a58-24f19b1ae3bc.jpg",
            "text": "<p>When wearing a nose pin, ensure that you take proper care to avoid any infections. Remove the nose pin while applying makeup and perfumes. Avoid wearing it while sleeping to avoid any discomfort.  </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_TVNiAi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When not wearing the nose pin, store it safely in a jewelry pouch and clean the nose pin every once in a while with a soft cloth. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7taxQg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>Adding a nose pin to your outfit can completely change your look. For ethnic wear, even a simple traditional nose stud can brings to life the desire to be truly desi and transform your look, and in western dresses, it enhances your beauty by looking elegant and accentuating your features. Choose a nose pin that redefines elegance, blends tradition and luxury. <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a> is crafted with enduring quality, ensuring the radiance remains intact for years. </p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
